USAGE: meliponto single <OPTIONS>

DESCRIPTION: Punches a single entrance in the ahgora system with the date and time provided by the flags.

OPTIONS:
	--date		d-m-yy		The date this punch will register <REQUIRED>
	--time		HH:mm		The time this punch will register <REQUIRED>
	--message	string		Message used to justify this punch [OPTIONAL]
	--token		string		When provided will be used to authenticate instead of prompting for your password [OPTIONAL]
	--help				Displays the help message for the command
